{{ja-kanjitab|いち|yomi=o}}
{{IPAfont|/iti/}} → {{IPAfont|/it͡ɕi/}}

Cognate with adverbs {{m|ja|甚|tr=ita, ito||[[very]], [[exceedingly]]}}.<ref name="DJS">{{R:Daijisen}}</ref><ref name="DJR">{{R:Daijirin}}</ref>

The use of this kanji is an example of phonetic {{ateji|sort=いち}},<ref name="DJR"/> possibly by extension of the "[[great]], [[superb]], [[outstanding]]" senses.

* {{ja-r|著しい|いちじるし.い}}
* {{ja-r|逸早|いちはや}}
* {{ja-r|逸早い|いちはやい}}
* {{ja-r|逸物|いちぶつ}}, {{ja-r|逸物|いちもつ}}

